data.description: Charming 4BR, 2.5BA Home in The Columns Subdivision! Step into elegance in this corner-lot gem! A columned foyer with hardwood floors welcomes you. The kitchen boasts new stainless appliances, granite countertops, and a walk-in pantry. The spacious master suite features dual vanities, walk-in closets, and a jetted tub. Entertain on the deck, and enjoy a neighborhood with access to a playground, lake, fishing pond, and park.
